She explained the new position of the High Representative for Foreign Affairs and Defence Policy as part of an answer to the question: "Who is who to the European Union?" "What phone number should I call?", so as an important step towards the uniqueness and greater readability of the Union's policy towards the states, such as China or India.
No one wants to ban us our syrecky (cooked cheese that smells very strong)
