Furthermore, he said that investigations in the impact zone do not report the appearance of ground parts.
"In one research, it was reported that there were no parts or components of the aircraft elsewhere, the impact was structurally presented.
"The helicopter had been designed for 19 passengers and met the requirements to carry them.
